            "title": "盤中速報 - 新華(5481)大跌7.25%，報23.65元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新華(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5481:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5481\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5481-TW</a>)16日09:00股價下跌1.85元，報23.65元，跌幅7.25%，成交247張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新華(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5481:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5481\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5481-TW</a>)所屬產業為其他業，主要業務為權利金收入。教材收入。其他。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌8.77%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.34%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><div class=\"dzbcd51\"></div><div class=\"m1aaic49\"></div><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-316 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-315 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-1 張</li> <li>融資增減：+56 張</li> <li>融券增減：+199 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
